<div class="card review_frm">
  <div class="card-body">
    <% if !post.agree_to_image_policy %>
      <p>
        The writer has not agreed to the image policy. Please reject this article and write "You have not agreed to the image policy" as the reason.
      </p>
    <% else %>
      <p>Make sure you've answered <b>yes</b> to all of the following criteria before accepting this article.</p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          Does this article follow the <a target="_blank" href="/pages/image-policy"><b>Image Policy</b></a>.<br>
        </li>
        <li>
          Does this article follow the <a target="_blank" href="/pages/content-policy"><b>Content Policy</b></a>?<br>
        </li>
        <li>
